      <section id="uid45">
        <title>Free Body Diagrams</title>
        <para id="id63576">In a free-body diagram, the object of interest is drawn as a dot and all the forces acting on it are drawn as arrows pointing away from the dot.
A free body diagram for the two-trailer-system will therefore look like this:</para>
