            <image mime-type="application/postscript" for="pdf" src="../../media/forces-and-motion-screenshot.eps" id="id63458_printimage"/>
            </media>
            </figure></para><section id="uid57">
        <title>Exercise</title>
        <list id="id64036" display="block" list-type="enumerated"><item id="uid58">A force acts on an object. Name three effects that the force can have on the object.
</item>
          <item id="uid59">Identify each of the following forces as contact or non-contact forces.
<list id="id64064" display="block" list-type="enumerated" number-style="lower-alpha"><item id="uid60">The force between the north pole of a magnet and a paper clip.
