          </item> <item> <label> Situation on Beeble in terms of situation on Earth </label>
          <para id="id80383">Write the equation for the gravitational force on Beeble and then substitute the values for <m:math overflow="scroll"><m:msub><m:mi>m</m:mi><m:mi>B</m:mi></m:msub></m:math> and <m:math overflow="scroll"><m:msub><m:mi>r</m:mi><m:mi>B</m:mi></m:msub></m:math>, in terms of the values for the Earth.</para>
