      <para id="id82499">The question explicitly gives</para>
      <list id="id82503" display="block" list-type="bulleted">
        <item id="uid344">the mass of the ball (<m:math overflow="scroll"><m:mi>m</m:mi></m:math> = 160 g = 0,16 kg), and
</item>
        <item id="uid345">the velocity of the ball (<m:math overflow="scroll"><m:mi>v</m:mi></m:math> = 40 m<m:math overflow="scroll"><m:mo>·</m:mo></m:math>s<m:math overflow="scroll"><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mrow><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:math>)
</item>
      </list>
      <para id="id82575">To calculate the momentum we will use</para>
