        <para id="id87342">It takes 8 s for the force to change the object's velocity from 2 m<m:math overflow="scroll"><m:mo>·</m:mo></m:math>s<m:math overflow="scroll"><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mrow><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:math>to the right to 6 m<m:math overflow="scroll"><m:mo>·</m:mo></m:math>s<m:math overflow="scroll"><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mrow><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msup></m:math>to the right. </para>
