        </item> <item> <label> Write the final answer </label>
        <para id="id94444">The torque from the perpendicular force is greater than the torque from the force applied at <m:math overflow="scroll"><m:msup><m:mn>60</m:mn><m:mo>∘</m:mo></m:msup></m:math>. Therefore, the best angle is <m:math overflow="scroll"><m:msup><m:mn>90</m:mn><m:mo>∘</m:mo></m:msup></m:math>. </para>
